# CHANGELOG & HISTORY

- v0.3.11
  - refined build_time
    - clear about cmake variable BUILD_TIMESTAMP is actually a cmake-configure-timestamp
    - add BUILD_TIME macro into config-base.hh so that backend can get a really compliing-time building timestamp. BUT, it has a M d yyyy date format, not a timestamp.
    - Finally, [cmdr-cxx](https://github.com/hedzr/cmdr-cxx) project updated cmdr::test::build_time() function to compliant with these changes.

- v0.3.10
  - improved `load-llvm`

- v0.3.9
  - fix `load-cmdr-cxx.cmake`

- v0.3.8
  - change exe-output-dir to `<root>/bin/<build-type>`
  - added a new post-build-action `target_add_post_copy_action` to link `<target-exe-file>` to `<root>/bin`
  - mv `cxx_set_ipo` into cxx-macros

- v0.3.7
  - make load-llvm deprecated
  - added new llvm-helpers, updated it
    - `add_llvm_target`, `add_llvm_test_target`
      - `add_llvm_supports`
        - `define_basics_llvm_target`
          - `llvm_config`

- v0.3.6
  - improved cxx-macros.cmake
    - add folder propertiy to exe, lib, test, example target for better view within cmake targets hirarchical structure

- v0.3.5
  - fix `versions-extract.py`

- v0.3.3
  - fix `versions-extract.py`, make it work for new style `.version.cmake` template
  - more

- v0.3.1
  - update `cxx-macros.cmake`
    - rename to `define_cxx_library_target`
    - rename to `define_cxx_executable_target`
    - add `IPO` switch to define_xxx
    - fix include-dirs in `define_cxx_executable_target`
    - fix include-dirs in `define_cxx_library_target`
    - fix include-dirs in `define_test_program`
    - add sanitizer to `define_cxx_executable_target`
    - add sanitizer to `define_cxx_library_target`
  - added `cxx-compilers-per-project.cmake`, which will be used in `define_cxx_library_target` & `define_cxx_executable_target`
  - added `debug_print_target_prop` to `debug-cmd.cmake`
  - update `cxx-detect-compilers.cmake`
  - update `utils.cmake`, fixed `debug_dump_target_inc_dirs`
  - update `versions-gen.cmake`, fix usage to `GIT_SHA`
  - update `packaging.cmake`, add usages to `PKG_GENERATOR` and `PACKAGING_GENERATOR`
  - update `prerequisites.cmake`, update ccache integrated section
